WEBVTT

00:00:04.525 --> 00:00:06.735 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Everyone wants to be happy.

00:00:08.112 --> 00:00:10.489 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But we all face problems,

00:00:10.489 --> 00:00:12.408 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
problems that are hard to deal with.

00:00:16.537 --> 00:00:19.790 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So can you ever really be happy?

00:00:28.007 --> 00:00:31.719 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At the 2020 convention
of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

00:00:31.719 --> 00:00:33.804 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you will learn how to find joy,

00:00:33.804 --> 00:00:36.098 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even when life is hard,

00:00:39.310 --> 00:00:41.353 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and how God has made it possible

00:00:41.353 --> 00:00:44.106 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for us to be happy now and forever!

00:00:48.277 --> 00:00:51.947 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Happiness might seem
hard to find, but it isn’t!

00:00:52.656 --> 00:00:54.700 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Come and see for yourself!

